2026-05-15T05:29:21.5458277Z 22    <!--
2026-05-15T05:29:21.5458611Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T05:29:21.5459028Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T05:29:21.5459422Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-15T05:29:21.5459932Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-15T05:29:21.5460433Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T05:29:21.5460968Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T05:29:21.5461518Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T05:29:21.5462076Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-15T05:29:21.5462632Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-15T05:29:21.5463129Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-15T05:29:21.5463534Z 33    -->
